    <h1> Going Green </h1>

<h2> What is "Going Green?" </h2> 
<p> Going green means going green means doing all of the things you can to preserve the environment such as conserving energy, saving money to protect the economy, reducing pollution and anything else you can think of that is more environmentally friendly than the convenient options </p>  
